{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_vrtx_01MkGU8os2EV7bScn7NFha5w","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Change Log\n2\t\n3\tA chronological record of all wiki operations.\n4\t\n5\t## 2026-07-09 — Ingested: Prompt Engineering Best Practices\n6\t- Created: prompt-engineering-best-practices.md — Core techniques: format specs, few-shot examples, chain-of-thought, sequential prompts, explicit constraints\n7\t- Cross-linked with: agent-eval-harness.md, skill-overlays.md, evaluator-super-agent.md\n8\t- Category: Machine Learning & AI\n9\t\n10\t## 2026-06-30 -- Ingested: Midpoint Check-in with Zack\n11\t- Created: midpoint-checkin-2026-06-30.md -- Halfway internship review: strengths (pioneering work, collaborative curiosity, handling ambiguity), opportunities (bigger picture thinking, report as product), energy management framework, career direction\n12\t- Cross-linked with: evaluator-super-agent.md, prototype-creator.md, ai-sdlc-pipeline.md\n13\t- Category: Meetings\n14\t- Note: Single-mic Gemini transcript, speakers reconstructed from context\n15\t\n16\t## 2026-06-29 -- Batch Ingestion: June 22-29 meetings + skill overlays\n17\t\n18\t**8 new wiki pages created:**\n19\t\n20\t1. **skill-overlays.md** -- LLM-generated project-specific context files (Carl Trieloff's team). Concept from Apr 2026, already showing accuracy gains.\n21\t   - Cross-linked with: evaluator-super-agent.md, agent-eval-harness.md, my-cursor-claw.md, ai-sdlc-pipeline.md\n22\t   - Category: Tools & Skills\n23\t\n24\t2. **andy-evan-2026-06-22.md** -- 1:1 review: eval scores improved 11→19, flagging system, Prototype Creator integration cost strategy ($25-30/run)\n25\t   - Cross-linked with: evaluator-super-agent.md, prototype-creator.md, ux-quality-rubric.md, andy-evan-eval-review-2026-06-16.md\n26\t   - Category: Meetings\n27\t\n28\t3. **standup-2026-06-22.md** -- Sprint capacity adjustments, customer engagement strategy, Archie CLI update\n29\t   - Cross-linked with: