vector DBs run\n- [Retrieval-Augmented Generation](retrieval-augmented-generation.md) — primary consumer of vector DB retrieval\n\n## Sources\n\n- sources/vector-databases.md\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":32,"oldLines":3,"newStart":32,"newLines":4,"lines":[" ## Sources"," "," - sources/vector-databases.md","+- Ingested: 2026-07-09 (updated: added pgvector)"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
